Q. Set Environment Paths for multiple python installations.
   go to search bar-->Edit the system environment variables-->Environment variables-->select system variables path or user variables path(your choice)
   go to path and give the path of your python and move up or down for preference.

Q. To know the default python version in windows.
   python --version

Q. Check the Python installations in your system(gives the path where it is installed).
   which python

Q. To get the system configuration.
   Windows + R ->> dxdiag
